				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{FE}} = \frac{{nFz}}{Q},$$\end{document}where z is the moles of product measured and Q is the total charge passed (C) at the time of sampling.
